Version 49.rc
~~~~~~~~~~~~~

We have headed to the big screen with a much anticipated fullscreen mode, in
part made possible by the ever-improving libadwaita.

A big focus this cycle has been error handling, to which end we now better
report errors to the user, complete with debug information for bug reports, 
and there also ‚Äî helped by much expanded unit testing ‚Äî should be far fewer
opportunities for things going awry in the first place.

This has also let to some improvements across Adwaita, Gtk, and GLib.

Thanks again to Alice Mikhaylenko, Anders Jonsson, Daniel Rusek,
Jordan Petridis, and Robert Kirkman, who all contributed to this release.

